---
// Hero component converted to Astro
---

<section class="w-full flex items-center justify-center py-20 md:py-32 min-h-[60vh] px-4">
    <div
        class="md:p-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-card border border-border rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-16 text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-xl"
    >
        <!-- Decorative background elements -->
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-20 -mr-20 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-20 -ml-20 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="text-center lg:text-start space-y-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full"
        >
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold">
                <span class="inline text-primary bg-clip-text">Grow your fleet with Haul.</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="text-xl text-white md:w-10/12 mx-auto lg:mx-0">
                We're looking for professional, reliable carriers to join our elite network. By
                partnering with Haul, you gain access to a massive pool of customers, advanced
                logistics tools, and a support team dedicated to your success.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-white md:w-10/12 mx-auto lg:mx-0">
                We handle the sales and technology, so you can focus on what you do best: moving.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-white md:w-10/12 mx-auto lg:mx-0">
                <strong>
                    Apply today to become a Haul certified carrier and start receiving jobs in your
                    area.
                </strong>
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
                <a
                    href="/book-a-move"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/80 w-full md:w-auto md:min-w-fit px-8 py-3"
                    aria-label="Get started with Haul moving services"
                >
                    Get Started
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
